response.overview: After being featured in our series nearly 10 years ago witht he Boeing 737-300 we're very happy to welcome Norwegian back this time with the Boeing 737-800. Winner of the best low cost airline award in Europe, Norwegian is growing fast both with the number of aircraft it operates and with the destinations it serves. We have a great program in store for you with some really interesting routes including a flight to the most Northerly airport in the world, some domestic flights in Norway, inter Scandinavian flights as well as flights to Germany & Italy. Enjoy some great crews who present their flights to you in details!
response.title: Norwegian 737-800 Top of the World
